To cite the GeoPDEs hierarchical package, please use

    E. M. Garau, R. Vazquez
    Algorithms for the implementation of adaptive
    isogeometric methods using hierarchical splines
    Appl. Numer. Math., 123:57-78, 2018.

The BibTeX entry for LaTeX users is:

@article{geopdes-hierarchical,
	title = {Algorithms for the implementation of adaptive isogeometric methods using hierarchical {B}-splines},
	year = {2018},
	keywords = {adaptive methods, coarsening, hierarchical splines, Isogeometric analysis, local refinement},
	author = {E.M. Garau and R. V{\'a}zquez},
        fjournal = {Applied Numerical Mathematics},
        journal = {Appl. Numer. Math.},
        volume = {123},
        pages = {58--87},
        doi = {10.1016/j.apnum.2017.08.006},
}

Algorithms for admissible refinement and coarsening are respectively given in

    C. Bracco, C. Giannelli, R. Vazquez 
    Refinement algorithms for adaptive isogeometric
    methods with hierarchical splines. 
    Axioms 7, 43, 2018.

    M. Carraturo, C. Giannelli, A. Reali, R. Vazquez 
    Suitably graded THB-spline refinement and coarsening: Towards 
    an adaptive isogeometric analysis of additive manufacturing processes. 
    Comput. Methods Appl. Mech. Engrg., 348:660-679, 2019.
